# Edge Computing and TinyML

## Overview

This laboratory explored deploying machine learning models on edge devices through model optimization techniques including pruning, quantization, and knowledge distillation.

## Technologies

- TensorFlow
- TensorFlow Lite
- TinyML
- Python

## Skills Developed

- Edge AI
- Model optimization
- Embedded AI deployment

## Learning Outcome

This project demonstrated how AI models can be compressed while maintaining performance for deployment on resource-constrained devices.
